    decode_data = base64.b64decode(encrypted_data)
    with open(
        path_save_private_key
        + nameFile.replace("(",'').replace(")",'').replace("," , "").replace("'",""), 
        'rb'
    ) as f:
        private_key = RSA.importKey(f.read())

    decrypted_data = cipher.decrypt(decode_data)
